title: Chal Chalein (Official Video) | Swapnanil Bhadra | Jimmy Roy | Chandan Mandal | New Release 2023
description:
Chal Chalein" is a new song that has both singing and dancing, and it's going to be a fun experience! The person who made it, Swapnanil Bhadra, was inspired by Michael Jackson. The song is about young love and having a good time without any worries or stress from social media or society. 

Starring the talented Jimmy Roy, "Chal Chalein" takes you on a journey of uninterrupted youth love and entertainment. With no social media crowds or societal pressures, this song is all about having a good time and letting loose.

The song has great music by Chandan Mandal and the lyrics were written by Chandan Mandal and Sanjay Sen. It's going to be really popular with young people. The song comes out on May 15th, 2023, and it will be available to watch and listen on GrooveNexus. Don't miss out on the fun!

title: Kya Loge Tum | Akshay Kumar | Amyra Dastur | BPraak | Jaani | Arvindr Khaira | Zohrajabeen
description:
Desi Melodies presents in association with Cape Of Good Films & Azeem Dayani the first single, 'Kya Loge Tum,' from B Praak's highly anticipated debut album, "Zohrajabeen." The star-studded team of B Praak, Jaani, Arvindr Khaira, and Akshay Kumar reunites for the first time since the pop-culture-defining songs 'Filhall' and 'Filhaal 2.'

The emotionally charged lyrics written by Jaani, along with his heart-wrenching composition, add an extra layer of depth to the already powerful track produced by B Praak himself. Arvindr Khaira takes it to the next level with his visionary direction, featuring Akshay Kumar and Amyra Dastur's palpable chemistry that will leave you wanting more.

Short Film "The way back home"

24:52 / 2023 / Japan
Writter / Director / Editor: Karin Miyagi
Cast: Rintaro Mizusawa, Takara Sakumoto, Teruhiro Tanaka, Sora Shiota, Kyanhitomi, Yoshi Sako and Masato Hagiwara
Original Story "The Two of Us, in a Town with a View of the Sea" by Kento Norikane

Synopsis:
Childhood friends Hinata and Hayato are training hard in kendo for their final high school inter-high school competition.
One day, Hinata is scouted by an entertainment agency. This causes a rift in their relationship.
The film depicts these two young boys who grow up to be adults while still carrying the pain & doubts from their youth.     

In 2022, the Japan Expo project was inaugurated to draw on the essence of cultures and tales that lie dormant in various areas of Japan and condense them into short stories. Short stories set in Iwate, Shizuoka & Fukuoka Prefectures were submitted & selected. 
At the SSFF & ASIA 2022 Fall Festival held in October 2022, a panel discussion was held with the invited writers of the stories. In addition, the short story "The Two of Us, in a Town with a View of the Sea" by Kento Norikane which was inspired by the novel "Konjiki Yasha" by writer Ozaki KÅyÅ, a famed author whose statue is in Atami City, has been adapted into a short film written & directed by Karin Miyagi and will be distributed worldwide through online screenings.

ATARA is a new Full On Psytrance project, founded by Israeli DJ and Producer Sigal Cohen.
Having passion for electronic music from an early age, playing in clubs and festivals from Israel to Budapest and Berlin, Sigal felt the need to express her own voice.
With this new project, she is going back to her roots to the powerfull sound of Psytrance she originally fell in love with as a child.
ATARA is known for her unique storytelling, Psychedelic melodies and Massive basslines - taking the listeners on a magical musical journey.

title: Malware - Tipos y cÃ³mo proteger tu PC
description:
Malware - Tipos y cÃ³mo proteger tu PC

Malware es el tÃ©rmino utilizado para identificar programas maliciosos o daÃ±inos para tu PC. El malware es un software que estÃ¡ destinado a daÃ±ar o deshabilitar computadoras y sistemas informÃ¡ticos. Para luchar contra el malware y proteger tu computadora, necesitas usar herramientas como antivirus, anti spywares y firewalls; muchos de los cuales se pueden encontrar de forma gratuita en la web. TambiÃ©n hay suites de seguridad completas disponibles para integrar a tu computadora Dell, lo que facilita enormemente la protecciÃ³n de tu sistema.

En este video hablaremos de los mÃ¡s comunes, cÃ³mo infectan tu computadora y cÃ³mo mantenerte protegido. 

AquÃ­ te mostramos algunos de los principales tipos de software maliciosos que pueden causar problemas importantes a tu sistema informÃ¡tico.

Virus
Un virus es un programa de capaz de autorreplicarse. Una vez que una computadora estÃ¡ infectada con un virus, Ã©ste puede propagarse a muchos otros archivos de tu computadora. Los virus se pueden propagar muy fÃ¡cilmente por Internet a travÃ©s de la descargas de archivos.

Worms o Gusanos
Un Worm es un tipo de malware ligeramente diferente. Al igual que los virus, pueden auto-replicarse, pero los gusanos son capaces de enviarse a sÃ­ mismos a muchas personas diferentes. Son muy peligrosos y pueden propagarse automÃ¡ticamente enviando mensajes a las personas de tu lista de contactos.

Troyanos
Un troyano tÃ©cnicamente no es un virus porque normalmente no puede hacer copias de sÃ­ mismo. Algunos troyanos se auto replican, pero generalmente son aplicaciones aparentemente Ãºtiles que has instalado que pueden abrir una puerta trasera secreta desde donde los hackers pueden ingresar y robar tu informaciÃ³n. La mayorÃ­a de las veces no tienes idea de que estÃ¡s infectado con un troyano.

Spyware
El spyware es similar a un troyano, pero en lugar de permitir que un pirata informÃ¡tico acceda a tu PC, lo espÃ­a silenciosamente. El spyware puede robar los nÃºmeros de tu tarjeta de crÃ©dito, informaciÃ³n de tu cuenta bancaria y cualquier otra informaciÃ³n confidencial y personal que tengas en tu computadora. A menudo estÃ¡ incluido con software de procedencia desconocida  para que se instale sin que te des cuenta.

Adware
Adware es bÃ¡sicamente lo mismo que Spyware, aunque no siempre es tan malicioso. Se instala en tu computadora e intenta mostrarte anuncios o publicidad relevante y de forma agresiva. Muchos de estos muestran tantos anuncios que pueden ralentizar su PC.
CÃ³mo Eliminar Adware de tu Navegador: https://dell.to/3s1UzVA 

Ransomware
El Ransomware amenaza con publicar tus datos o bloquea continuamente el acceso a ellos a menos que se pague un rescate. Mientras que algunos ransomware simples pueden bloquear el sistema pero no requiere mucho para desbloquearlo, otros ransomwares mÃ¡s avanzados usan una tÃ©cnica llamada "extorsiÃ³n viral criptogrÃ¡fica" que encripta los archivos de la vÃ­ctima, haciÃ©ndolos virtualmente inaccesibles.

title: Unearthing Gold: Victoria Gold's Eagle Mine on Track for Success!
description:
Successful Q1 production of 37,000 oz of gold highlights ability to stack ore year-round and signals favourable market conditions

Victoria Gold is a mining company that owns the Eagle Gold mine in Canada's Yukon territory. They produced 37,000oz of gold in Q1 and aim to produce up to 200,000oz annually. They have demonstrated their ability to stack large amounts of ore on the leach pad year-round, indicating a long mine life for producing gold. The timing of the high gold prices is favourable for the company.

John McConnell

John McConnell's +40 years of mining experience is mostly in Canada's northern territories. Previously, he was President & CEO of Western Keltic Mines until it was acquired by Sherwood Copper; VP, NWT Projects for De Beers Canada primarily responsible for permitting and development of the Snap Lake Diamond Mine; Breakwater Resources Ltd in operations at the Nanisivik Zinc & Lead Mine on Baffin Island; and Strathcona Mineral Services Ltd.

Mr. McConnell is the 2021 Winner of AME BC's prestigious EA Scholtz Award for Excellence in Mine Development for his role in building the Eagle Gold mine.

A graduate of the Colorado School of Mines, with a B.Sc. in Mining Engineering Mr. McConnell is also a Director of Lahontan Gold Corp and Abacus Mining & Exploration Corp.

title: The Big Bear Yawn
description:
Learn more about our work at https://www.mycalmworld.com/.  

The Big Bear Yawn is an interactive bedtime routine that reminds us that the best sleep schedule can be achieved by preparing ourselves properly for rest.  

Written and performed by Shanna Forrestall, with original music by Jeff Gold, custom illustrations by Kayla Silverstein, and featuring the Big Bear played by actor Escalante Lundy, this important story will give you a simple guide to bedtime that encourages YOUR cubs to celebrate the steps while they prepare to hibernate for the night.

Be sure to subscribe.  Check out our stories and songs on Youtube or your favorite streaming app - we help families find their calm.   http://www.MyCalmWorld.com 
----
The Big Bear Yawn:

The big bear used to swear he had trouble falling asleep
But then he learned a simple Trick to help him go down deep

He starts his bedtime ritual by brushing his big bear teeth
Then he washes his big bear fur before he slides into his clean bed sheets

He pats his big bear pillow to make it soft and pretends itâ€™s a cloud
He lowers his big bear voice to be very quiet instead of loud.

He gently crawls into his big bear bed and lays his furry body down.
He makes sure he has a smile on his face instead of a sour frown

He breathes in a deep big bear breath and lets out a big bear sigh
He wraps himself in his big bear blanket with his peaceful paws at his side

And then when his ritual is all complete and his big bear worries are gone.
He finally relaxes deeply and lets out his big bear yawn.

Yawwwnnnn.... 

Good night big bear
Good night little bear
Good night to the baby bears too

Good night big bear
Good night Little bear
We are so proud of you
.

.
